{
  "stem": "5103.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But somehow, it was just at the time-- it must have been our luck-- it was just at the time when all that transportation was going on, and they were checking all the people, because sometimes they were checking in the trucks, big trucks, to see if they were hiding anybody in amongst the food and things, in bales of things, hay and whatever.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as this was our luck, as this was going on, the fellow was so interested to see that everything was going all right for the big trucks, and whatever was going on around him, that when he saw us three bedraggled looking people, I suppose, he just-- my father had his papers out, his card, that said Johannes [?",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Peter Bink ?] and where we was coming from, and he had to go there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he just marched on, and-- and he looked at me, and I, you know, smiled, and sort of did exactly what I was told, and we marched along with the cart, and my mother sort of looking down.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember thinking at the time, if we make it across the bridge, we'll make it, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And once we got that first stop down, we made it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we got to this family, Mien and Jan Baay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father had been there already once, so he knew what he was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were nice people, very nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was distant relative, as I say, because of my grandmother's side of the family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They was, like, a very distant, cousin of a cousin, who was married to a non-Jewish man, and who had had children, so the children were not Jewish at all.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was like a big thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they said, yes, we will keep you.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
